Heneka comments / shifs / modifications integrated

v15
Heneka comments / shifs / modifications integrated
EBUCore based on Dublin Core + SKOS + some BBC Core Concepts + basic FOAF properties  + equivalences to W3C MA-ONT

Corrections following feedback from Europeana for the re-use of audio properties: fileByteSize and fileSize are redundant with a common definition -> removal of fileByteSize. Clarification of bitRate: refined definition (bits per second and not kbps) to address both constant and variable bitrate -> removal of redundant averageBitRate transformed into bitRateMax in bps. Add subproperties hasMimeType and hasAudioEncodingFormat to ebucore_hasFormat to match the subclasses defined under skos:Concept. New relations: hasRelatedEvent and hasRelatedLocation. resourceName domain changed from MediaResource to Resource.
Generated using the ASSAM OWL export module. Modified by Swapna Oundhakar for MWSDF.
